{
  "stem": "12289.1",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It is spelled A-N-G-E-R.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Per, P-E-R.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The 7th of December, 1913.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I am now 82.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was born in Goteborg, in the-- on the Swedish west coast.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I was-- we were living-- my parents were living in Goteborg when I was very, very small.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was only three years old.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I don't have any recollections, really, from Goteborg.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My father was an engineer and was working in the-- constructing the-- the harbor and the streets in Goteborg.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he was then-- he moved to Stockholm, where he got a similar job in Stockholm.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we lived then, from when I was four years old, to a house on the southern part of Stockholm, where it was like being in the country, at that time.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, now it has changed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The whole picture has changed, now, of course.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my whole childhood is, there, on the southern part, just along the-- the-- the harbor of Stockholm, the outskirts of the harbors, should I say, when-- where I had a very happy childhood.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were two brothers, at that time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we-- I went then to primary school, first, in the-- in the southern part of Stockholm and then to the-- the high school and that.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "See, that part of Sweden, of Stockholm was-- was considered to be rather a-- not a proletariat, sort of a poor part of Stockholm.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it wasn't as-- as up-- there wasn't the 'upper tens' who lived there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we lived there, because my father's job was just building a canal outside Stockholm at that part.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So that's why we lived there.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
